  "title": "ArmorPlus",
  "description": "ArmorPlus is a mod based on exploration, killing, building, getting geared up, fight the bosses and explore the depths of your worlds",
  "body": "<p><img src=\"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/sokratis12GR/ArmorPlus/1.9.4/headerimg.jpg\" alt=\"ArmorPlus Banner-Logo\" /></p>\n<h4 id=\"armorplus-is-a-mod-which-introduces-brand-new-multi-tiered-arsenal-to-your-minecraft-world-each-with-its-own-unique-abilities-so-that-they-can-all-be-utilized-to-the-fullest-depending-on-the-different-situations-your-journeys-may-encounter\"><strong>ArmorPlus is a mod which introduces brand new multi-tiered arsenal to your Minecraft world, each with its own unique abilities so that they can all be utilized to the fullest depending on the different situations your journeys may encounter.</strong></h4>\n<h4 id=\"it-also-adds-some-world-generation-to-ensure-that-you-will-always-have-something-new-to-explore\"><strong>It also adds some world generation to ensure that you will always have something new to explore.</strong></h4>\n<h3>─────────────────────────</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://nodecraft.com/r/armorplus\"><img src=\"https://nodecraft.com/assets/images/about/branding/logo-on-white-download.png\" alt=\"Nodecraft Sponsor\" width=\"500\" height=\"500\" /></a></p>\n<h5 id=\"this-project-is-sponsored-by-nodecraft-use-code-armorplus-for-30-off-your-first-month-of-service\"><strong>This project is sponsored by Nodecraft. Use code <a href=\"https://nodecraft.com/r/armorplus\"><strong>ArmorPlus</strong></a>&nbsp;for 30% off your first month of service!</strong></h5>\n<h3>─────────────────────────</h3>\n<h3 id=\"dependencies\"><strong>Dependencies</strong></h3>\n<h4 id=\"118x-thedragonlib--geckolib-30\"><strong>1.19.x:&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.curseforge.com/minecraft/mc-mods/thedragonlib/files\">TheDragonLib</a> |&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.curseforge.com/minecraft/mc-mods/geckolib\">GeckoLib 3.0</a></strong></h4>\n<h4 id=\"118x-thedragonlib--geckolib-30\"><strong>1.18.x:&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.curseforge.com/minecraft/mc-mods/thedragonlib/files\">TheDragonLib</a> |&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.curseforge.com/minecraft/mc-mods/geckolib\">GeckoLib 3.0</a></strong></h4>\n<h4 id=\"116x-thedragonlib--geckolib-30\"><strong>1.16.x: <a href=\"https://www.curseforge.com/minecraft/mc-mods/thedragonlib/files\">TheDragonLib</a> |&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.curseforge.com/minecraft/mc-mods/geckolib\">GeckoLib 3.0</a>&nbsp;<span style=\"color: #ff00ff;\">(Soon to be Out of Support)</span></strong></h4>\n<h4 id=\"112x-thedragonlib\"><strong>1.12.x: <a href=\"https://www.curseforge.com/minecraft/mc-mods/thedragonlib/files\">TheDragonLib</a>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;<span style=\"color: #ff0000;\">(Out of Support)</span></strong></h4>\n<h4 id=\"111x-thedragonlib--forgelin\"><strong>1.11.x: <a href=\"https://www.curseforge.com/minecraft/mc-mods/thedragonlib/files\">TheDragonLib</a> | <a href=\"https://www.curseforge.com/minecraft/mc-mods/shadowfacts-forgelin\">Forgelin</a>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;<span style=\"color: #ff0000;\">(Out of Support)</span></strong></h4>\n<h3>─────────────────────────</h3>\n<h3 id=\"in-game-item--block-showcase\"><strong>In-Game Item &amp; Block Showcase</strong></h3>\n<p><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/AzDxERr.png\" alt=\"ArmorPlus Lava &amp; Frost Crystal Blocks &amp; Ores\" width=\"1080\" /> <img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/TAEqXrt.png\" alt=\"ArmorPlus Coal Equipment &amp; Items\" width=\"1080\" /> <img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/smkpqDk.png\" alt=\"ArmorPlus Redstone Equipment &amp; Items\" width=\"1080\" /> <img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/e3aExgi.png\" alt=\"ArmorPlus Lapis Equipment &amp; Items\" width=\"1080\" /> <img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/HTfOu08.png\" alt=\"ArmorPlus Emerald Equipment &amp; Items\" width=\"1080\" /> <img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/3CqMmqM.png\" alt=\"ArmorPlus Enriched Obsidian Equipment &amp; Items\" width=\"1080\" /> <img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/6aeq9Tg.png\" alt=\"ArmorPlus Infused Lava Equipment &amp; Items\" width=\"1080\" /> <img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/8tM7Y8Q.png\" alt=\"ArmorPlus Guardian Equipment &amp; Items\" width=\"1080\" /> <img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/jIPbeNj.png\" alt=\"ArmorPlus Super Star Equipment &amp; Items\" width=\"1080\" /> <img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/ykkl9lg.png\" alt=\"ArmorPlus Ender Dragon Equipment &amp; Items\" width=\"1080\" /> <img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/YvJbbRu.png\" alt=\"ArmorPlus Slayer Equipment &amp; Items\" width=\"1080\" /></p>\n<h3>─────────────────────────</h3>\n<h3 id=\"video-showcasespotlights\"><strong>Video Showcase/Spotlights</strong></h3>\n<p><iframe allowfullscreen=\"allowfullscreen\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/Mw5qJg-FQ6s\" height=\"500\" width=\"100%\"></iframe></p>\n<h3>─────────────────────────</h3>\n<h3 id=\"screenshots-of-items-via-jei\"><strong>Screenshots of Items (via JEI)</strong></h3>\n<h4><strong>1.18.2</strong></h4>\n<p><iframe allowfullscreen=\"allowfullscreen\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/dQ2QLAs1j6M\" height=\"315\" width=\"560\"></iframe></p>\n<h4 id=\"1102\"><strong>1.10.2</strong></h4>\n<p><img src=\"https://i.gyazo.com/a26492549a2b001c352ede5ce06c8e0a.gif\" alt=\"\" /></p>\n<h3>─────────────────────────</h3>\n<h3 id=\"modpacks\"><strong>Modpacks</strong></h3>\n<h3><a href=\"https://minecraft.curseforge.com/projects/project-ozone-3-a-new-way-forward\"><strong>Featured on Project Ozone 3</strong></a></h3>\n<h3>─────────────────────────</h3>\n<h3 id=\"mod-integrations\"><strong>Mod Integrations</strong></h3>\n<h5 id=\"armorplus-has-added-integration-with\"><strong>ArmorPlus has added integration with:</strong></h5>\n<p><a href=\"https://minecraft.curseforge.com/projects/jei\"><strong>JEI (Just Enough Items)</strong></a>: Workbench, High-Tech Bench, Ulti-Tech Bench &amp; The Champion Bench&nbsp;<strong>(Not 1.16.5+)</strong></p>\n<p><a href=\"https://minecraft.curseforge.com/projects/the-one-probe\"><strong>TOP (The One Probe)</strong></a>: Support for all of the ArmorPlus helmets&nbsp;<strong>(Not 1.16.5+)</strong></p>\n<p><a href=\"https://minecraft.curseforge.com/projects/tesla\"><strong>Tesla</strong></a>: The tesla tools &amp; steel armor <strong>(Not 1.12.2+)</strong></p>\n<p><strong>RF (Embemed)</strong>: The RF tools &amp; Steel armor <strong>(Not 1.11.2+)</strong></p>\n<p><a href=\"https://minecraft.curseforge.com/projects/tinkers-construct\"><strong>Tinkers' Construct</strong></a>: Some materials and modifiers like Lava Crystal (Material)</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://minecraft.curseforge.com/projects/projecte\"><strong>ProjectE (EMC)</strong></a>: A configurable option to make almost everything in the mod to contain EMC value (enable it via armorplus/integrations.cfg)&nbsp;<strong>(Not 1.16.5+)</strong></p>\n<p><a href=\"https://minecraft.curseforge.com/projects/crafttweaker\"><strong>CraftTweaker</strong></a>: All of the benches and the lava infuser have CT support&nbsp;<strong>(Not 1.16.5+)</strong></p>\n<h6 id=\"how-to-use-the-crafttweaker-integration\"><strong>How to use the CraftTweaker Integration</strong></h6>\n<p><a href=\"https://gist.github.com/sokratis12GR/4a56e48af0d49b5d832fb22ebc8ce56b\"><strong>Click Here for a detailed explanation</strong></a></p>\n<h3>─────────────────────────</h3>\n<h3 id=\"faq\"><strong>FAQ:</strong></h3>\n<p><strong>Q: I found a Bug/Glitch/Error What i need to do ?</strong></p>\n<p>A: Report it at the issue tracker here:&nbsp;<a href=\"https://github.com/sokratis12GR/ArmorPlus\">https://github.com/sokratis12GR/ArmorPlus</a></p>\n<p><strong>Q: I want to donate to support your development, how can I do so ?</strong></p>\n<p>A: You can support us by donating via this page <a href=\"http://paypal.me/sokratis12GR\">http://paypal.me/sokratis12GR</a> (PayPal.me)</p>\n<p><strong>Q: Can i repost this mod in other websites ?</strong></p>\n<p>A: No, You aren't allowed to repost any versions of this mod to other websites.</p>\n<p><strong>Q: Am I allowed to use this mod's textures or any art work ?</strong></p>\n<p>A: No.</p>\n<h3>─────────────────────────</h3>\n<h4 id=\"modpack-permissions-link-to-them\"><strong>Modpack Permissions (<a href=\"https://github.com/sokratis12GR/ArmorPlus/blob/1.16.5/ModPack%20Licence.md\">Link to them</a>)</strong></h4>\n<h3>─────────────────────────</h3>\n<h3 id=\"want-to-support-us\"><strong>Want to support us?</strong></h3>\n<p><strong>You can support us in many ways, including donating to us, or becoming a patreon.</strong>&nbsp;</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.patreon.com/sokratis12GR\"><img src=\"https://s3-us-west-1.amazonaws.com/widget-images/become-patron-widget-medium%402x.png\" width=\"200\" /></a></p>\n<h3 id=\"social-links\"><strong>Social Links</strong></h3>\n<h5 id=\"twitter\"><strong>Twitter</strong></h5>\n<p><a href=\"https://twitter.com/sokratis12GR\"><strong>Follow us on twitter @sokratis12GR</strong></a></p>\n<h5 id=\"discord\"><strong>Discord</strong></h5>\n<p><a title=\"ArmorPlus Community Server\" href=\"https://discord.gg/JCWbJvA\"><strong>Join our ArmorPlus Discord Community Server, Join via: https://discord.gg/JCWbJvA</strong></a></p>",
